{"word":"G4411 - πρωτοκλισία - prōtoklisía - pro-tok-lis-ee'-ah - Chief","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πρωτοκλισία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prōtoklisía</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pro-tok-lis-ee'-ah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Chief</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"முதன்மையான இடம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"the first reclining - place, the chief place"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4413 - πρῶτος - prōtos - pro'-tos/4413\">G4413</a> and <a href=\"#/G2828 - κλισία - klisía - klee-see'-ah/2828\">G2828</a>; a <i>reclining first</i> (in the place of honor) at the dinner bed, that is, <i>preeminence</i> at meals: - chief (highest, uppermost) room.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4409/4409\">G4409</a>, <a href=\"#/G4410/4410\">G4410</a>, <a href=\"#/G4411/4411\">G4411</a>, <a href=\"#/G4412/4412\">G4412</a>, <a href=\"#/G4413/4413\">G4413</a>, <a href=\"#/G4414/4414\">G4414</a>, <a href=\"#/G4415/4415\">G4415</a>, <a href=\"#/G4416/4416\">G4416</a>"}]}